{"tid":571861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"才坦言喜歡做愛和錢　AV女優再挑戰業界大忌","createTime":"2018-02-25T05:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T21:27:46.000Z","uid":25345,"like":134,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"d658218a7f817e13a778317df2094bb7d3930bf5","tid":571861,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T05:27:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180110/640_c74c033bed62cba147a083251b6f984b.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180110%2F640_c74c033bed62cba147a083251b6f984b.jpg&d=NohmppOcrP8OYqKDbJf%2BYL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=5bb00459\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180110/640_c74c033bed62cba147a083251b6f984b.jpg</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180110/640_1a5321e9b7c07b680b8bd87691ef6d8a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180110%2F640_1a5321e9b7c07b680b8bd87691ef6d8a.jpg&h=7963e2d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180110/640_523b90bbba955089e1408fb399a061eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180110%2F640_523b90bbba955089e1408fb399a061eb.jpg&h=f992c3e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAV女優抽菸會減損你的支持嗎？20歲的日本AV女優淺田結梨，日前才在《推特》與網友對答時，坦承自己因為喜歡做愛和錢才拍AV，想不到昨天更大膽，直接挑戰業界大忌，po出自己「太妹蹲」的拿香菸照片。<br />\n<br />\nAV達人「一劍浣春秋」在《PLAY NO.1》網站發文指出，儘管日本女生抽菸比例很高，但AV女優為了避免影迷討厭，都知道絕對不能在影迷面前抽菸，「所以看到浅田結梨在直播時抽菸給大家看我超震撼的，而且她還用太妹蹲姿抽菸！」、「她失控了」。<br />\n<br />\n一劍浣春秋表示，自己偶爾會接到AV女優經紀人要求刪除照片的要求，不是因為AV女優被拍配，而且因為她們口袋露出方形盒子的痕跡，也就是會被看出是香菸，所以他認為淺田結梨此舉不太聰明，「少了人氣，就會沒有買氣，沒有買氣，就不會有片商想要投資」、「只能希望此舉對她沒有太大傷害」。"},{"pid":"98a1d7895bca04c36fb74fea084224345ea5c870","tid":571861,"uid":8867,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T05:28:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27bd1f34420